I noticed that you have duplicate server-profile-modal divs and also duplicate "TOP 15 MODS VISUAL MEJORADA" sections in your HTML. Having duplicate IDs and repeated content can lead to unexpected behavior and makes your code harder to maintain.

I have removed the duplicate instances of these elements and consolidated the related scripts. Additionally, I've implemented the loadServerProfile function for the server modal, making it dynamic as intended.

Here's the cleaned-up and corrected HTML:

